*   ## **_WILL OSPREAY VS RICOCHET GOES TO A DRAW; RESTARTED THEN GOES TO A NO CONTEST THANKS TO TAKESHITA INTERFERENCE_**
    

Make no mistake about it. Both men moved like it was 2016. A dead even match where both men looked incredible.

Konosuke Takeshita plays spoil sport and takes out both men to ruin this match and stand tall over them.

